50:04.469 --> 50:06.147
- So you did get in trouble?

50:06.171 --> 50:08.582
- Kids get in trouble for that
kind of stuff all the time.

50:08.606 --> 50:10.051
- Yeah?

50:10.075 --> 50:12.253
I mean when I get in
trouble my dad just,

50:12.277 --> 50:14.488
I don't know, he
just chews me out.

50:14.512 --> 50:16.523
Sometimes he'll listen
when it's important to me

50:16.547 --> 50:19.260
but I've noticed that
when you get in trouble

50:19.284 --> 50:21.286
you just kinda become
Clarise's servant.

50:22.853 --> 50:25.666
Maybe what Maxton shoulda
done, and what any friend

50:25.690 --> 50:28.302
including me, should
do, is walk you in

50:28.326 --> 50:30.537
and take the blame
for making you late

50:30.561 --> 50:32.306
because chances are
at that point Clarise

50:32.330 --> 50:35.176
will kind of back way
down and be less harsh.

50:35.200 --> 50:36.643
Maybe in the end...

50:36.667 --> 50:38.412
- In the end she would
just wait for you to leave

50:38.436 --> 50:39.780
and then just chew
me out anyways.

50:40.638 --> 50:41.638
- Hey, Bryant.

50:45.176 --> 50:46.287
- Why is he with Indy?

50:46.311 --> 50:47.345
- Ugh.

50:49.247 --> 50:51.816
- Come on, we should
probably get you home.

50:55.853 --> 50:57.431
- There's no way I can lie now,

50:57.455 --> 50:59.300
