saw us at the park.

50:59.324 --> 51:00.534
- You'll be fine.

51:00.558 --> 51:02.627
- Speak of the devil.

51:04.129 --> 51:05.239
- I'm here.

51:05.263 --> 51:07.508
- No, Bryant, just go home.

51:07.532 --> 51:08.532
I'll be fine, okay?

51:11.536 --> 51:12.813
What are you doing?

51:12.837 --> 51:14.472
- Exactly what I
should be doing.

51:15.906 --> 51:17.284
Hey, Mrs. Taylor.

51:17.308 --> 51:18.185
- Hi, Bryant.

51:18.209 --> 51:20.521
My girls said they
saw you at the park.

51:20.545 --> 51:21.755
They just left for the mall,

51:21.779 --> 51:23.490
they'll be so sad
they missed you.

51:23.514 --> 51:25.283
- Oh, well, tell 'em I say hi.

51:29.220 --> 51:31.198
Are we too late?

51:31.222 --> 51:32.766
Were you looking for Indy?

51:32.790 --> 51:34.301
- You know I was.

51:34.325 --> 51:36.303
Yesterday she was so
late getting home

51:36.327 --> 51:39.264
that I just wanted to make
sure she made it home today.

51:41.399 --> 51:42.309
- Do you need me to stay?

51:42.333 --> 51:45.312
- Oh, Indy will be
just fine without you.

51:45.336 --> 51:47.781
Now go ahead and have a
seat in the living room.

51:47.805 --> 51:49.307
- Thank you for walking me home.

52:00.385 --> 52:03.164
- You're walking on very
thin ice right now.

52:03.188 --> 52:04.798
I don't know what it is
you're trying to prove

52:04.822 --> 52:06.500
with Bryant Bailey but remember

52:06.524 --> 52:10.237
he is only being nice to you
because he killed your cat.

52:10.261 --> 52:12.539
My girls have had their
eyes on him for years

52:12.563 --> 52:15.242
and the last thing I need is
you getting in Jayda's way

52:15.266 --> 52:17.844
especially with prom
right around the corner.

52:17.868 --> 52:19.546
Go do your chores.

52:19.570 --> 52:21.172
We'll talk about this later.

52:23.441 --> 52:24.441
- Yes, ma'am.

52:37.555 --> 52:38.765
Hello?

52:38.789 --> 52:40.267
- Hey, what happened?

52:40.291 --> 52:42.603
- Nothing I haven't
heard before.

52:42.627 --> 52:44.338
- Well, let me know
if it gets bed.

52:44.362 --> 52:46.273
- I'm sure everything
will be okay.

52:46.297 --> 52:47.398
- I'm serious.

52:48.266 --> 52:49.610
- Okay.

52:49.634 --> 52:50.877
- Wanna walk to school tomorrow?

52:50.901 --> 52:52.946
- I actually probably shouldn't

52:52.970 --> 52:55.849
I have to go to Maxton's
soccer game on Saturday

52:55.873 --> 52:58.319
and I wouldn't wanna be
grounded before then.

52:58.343 --> 53:00.245
But, Bryant?

53:02.313 --> 53:03.957
Thank you.

53:03.981 --> 53:04.981
- Anytime.

53:05.650 --> 53:06.693
- Goodnight.

53:06.717 --> 53:10.931
- Goodnight.

